name: Android Dreams #2 Monolith
description: Artist: Skryptiq | Tools: Rhino, Grasshopper, Houdini, Blender, JPEG: 2880x3600 pixels | Original Creation Date: April 15, 2021 | Twitter: @skryptiq This series explores artificial intelligences which take cues from natural processes. 3d geometry is given agency and allowed to self-organize based on a pre-determined set of rules to produce outcomes which are neither the product of pure algorithms or top-down design decisions.
